    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior has significant damage, including heavy rusting on the door panels, multiple large dents, and peeling clear coat across the hood and roof. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission shifts harshly; it will likely require major repairs or a full overhaul to be reliable. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor.",
